        OH_MY_GOB_YOU_RE_ONE_OF_THOSE                                         = 7609,  -- Oh my Gob! You're one of those adventurerurers, aren't ya? You got nothin' on me, man./lady.] I was just mindin' my own businesesess, lookin' for junk an' stuff.
        HEY_WATCH_OUT_YOU_DON_T_WANNA_FIGHT                                   = 7610,  -- Hey, watch out. You don't wanna fight me. I'll turn you into meat jerky! Wait, how about you and me be friends instead? Sound good?
        I_TRAVEL_ALL_OVER_THE_WORLD_AND_HEAR                                  = 7611,  -- I travel all over the world and hear lots of differererent stories. I even hear your stories. I can tell you one, if you want.
