        LISTEN                                                                = 7617,  -- .........listen......
        OH_OUTTA_HERE                                                         = 7618,  -- Oh...... ...outta here.........
        DO_YOU_WANT_TO_HEAR_A_STORY_NO                                        = 7619,  -- Do you want to hear a story? No, thank you. Let's hear one.
        WHAT_STORY_WOULD_YOU_LIKE_TO_BE_TOLD                                  = 7620,  -- What story would you like to be told? On second thought, maybe later. Full Fields. Green Groves. Mining Missive. Pond Probing. Coastal Chaos. Seed Sowing. Flotsam Finding(pt.1). Flotsam Finding(pt.2). Kit Empathizer. Jingly Dangler. Mole Manipulator. Hypnotic Hospitality. Titillating Tomes(pt.1). Titillating Tomes(pt.2). Release the Fleece. Feeding Frenzy. Cry Not, Caretaker(pt.1). Cry Not, Caretaker(pt.2). Chacharoon's Cheer(pt.1). Chacharoon's Cheer(pt.2). Trial of the Chacharoon(pt.1). Trial of the Chacharoon(pt.2). Doctor Chacharoon(pt.1). Doctor Chacharoon(pt.2). Rowing Together(pt.1). Rowing Together(pt.2). Glittering Gals(pt.1). Glittering Gals(pt.2). Sally Forth!(pt.1). Sally Forth!(pt.2).
        HOW_INCREDIBLY_INTREPID_OF_YOU_TO_INQUEST_INTO                        = 7624,  -- How incredibly intrepid of you to inquest into this island plot. Welcome to your well-deserved Mog Garden, kupo!
        DID_YOU_TOIL_TIRELESSLY_TRYING_TO_AMASS_AGRARIAN                      = 7625,  -- Did you toil tirelessly trying to amass agrarian assets in your Mog House, or did your knees start knocking at the very mention of gathering goods? Either way, Mog Gardens have proven positively pleasant for all pioneers!
        AS_AN_EMBLEM_OF_OUR_ETERNAL_ESTEEM_FOR                                = 7626,  -- As an emblem of our eternal esteem for each other--and to elicit enthusiasm for this endeavor--allow me to present you with %, kupo! Each day that elapses (in Earth time), you're served a star!
        THE_MORE_REFULGENCES_RESIDING_IN_THIS_ROCK_THE                        = 7627,  -- The more refulgences residing in this rock, the richer the rewards you'll reap. But first, let's learn about the myriad methods by which you make use of your Mog Garden!
        NO_NEED_TO_SWEAT_SABERS_OVER_YOUR_NEOPHYTE                            = 7628,  -- No need to sweat sabers over your neophyte knowledge of Mog Gardens, kupo! Leave everything to mister moogle here and his go-getting green thumb.
        WE_BEGIN_WITH_THE_BARE_BASICS_LET_S                                   = 7629,  -- We begin with the bare basics. Let's get going on grasping that grandiose garden of yours.
        TO_BE_MORE_PRECISE_IT_MAY_BEHOOVE_YOU                                 = 7630,  -- To be more precise, it may behoove you to barge into that basket over there, kupo.
        BACK_IN_YOUR_MOG_HOUSE_I_BET_GARDENING                                = 7631,  -- Back in your Mog House, I bet gardening was a chore. Here, however, it's a delightful diversion from the wild and woolly world outside.
        SIMPLY_STICK_YOUR_SNOUT_IN_THAT_BASKET_OVER                           = 7632,  -- Simply stick your snout in that basket over there, and declare your discoveries to me.
        CONGRATULATIONS_ON_HAULING_IN_YOUR_HEADMOST_HARVEST_DON               = 7633,  -- Congratulations on hauling in your headmost harvest! Don't forget, all that palatable produce and paraphernalia is yours for the picking, kupo.
        KUPOPOPO_I_SENSE_SOME_SEEDLINGS_OF_INFORMATION_SPROUTING              = 7634,  -- Kupopopo... I sense some seedlings of information sprouting.
        UNLIKE_AT_MOG_HOUSES_LEAVING_THE_FRUITS_OF                            = 7635,  -- Unlike at Mog Houses, leaving the fruits of your labor to languish on the vine won't dry them out like Hildebert's sense of humor, kupo.
        WHA_WHA_WHAT_THEY_WOULDN_T_WITHER_IF                                  = 7636,  -- Wha-wha-what? They wouldn't wither if we moogles watched over them properly, you proffer?
        PISH_POSH_WE_RE_ON_OUR_BEST_BEHAVIOR                                  = 7637,  -- Pish posh! We're on our best behavior when it comes to caring for crops, kupo!
        OWOWOW_I_SUPPOSE_THE_TRUTH_TRULY_DOES_HURT                            = 7638,  -- Owowow... I suppose the truth truly does hurt, kupo.
        SO_THE_FEROCIOUSLY_FIRM_FRUIT_THAT_PLUNKED_ME                         = 7639,  -- So...the ferociously firm fruit that plunked me on my pom-pom fell from that flora?
        BUT_HOW_COULD_IT_HAVE_COME_SO_FAR                                     = 7640,  -- But how could it have come so far? Did wild winds whip in from the Senroh Sea just to dent my dome? How devilishly disconcerting, kupo!
        WE_HAVE_TO_CORRAL_THESE_CRANIUM_CRIPPLING_CONUNDRUMS                  = 7641,  -- We have to corral these cranium-crippling conundrums before they bonk any more bystanders!
        EXAMINE_THE_RUSTIC_ROOTS_GROWING_FROM_THAT_GREEN                      = 7642,  -- %, examine the rustic roots growing from that green grove to extirpate the extraneous and evildoing edibles! Trust me. It may seem irrelevant, but it'll actually help us get to the root of the problem. Kupopopo!
        EXAMINE_THE_EARTH_RUPTURING_ROOTS_TO_REVEAL_RIVETING                  = 7643,  -- Examine the earth-rupturing roots to reveal riveting rewards!
        WELL_MAYBE_NOT_RIVETING_BUT_REWARDS_NONETHELESS_KUPO                  = 7644,  -- Well, maybe not riveting, but rewards nonetheless, kupo. Either way, take some time to talk to me when you're done.
        THANK_YOU_FOR_COLLECTING_THOSE_CURSED_COMESTIBLES_FEEL                = 7645,  -- Thank you for collecting those cursed comestibles. Feel free to keep any and all you find hereafter for your culinary consumption.
        AS_AN_ASIDE_SHOULD_YOU_LACK_LIGNEOUS_LIBATIONS                        = 7646,  -- As an aside, should you lack ligneous libations, logging will lay you up with some %, kupo.
        UNDULATING_UMBRILS_WHAT_IN_THE_WORLD_WAS_THAT                         = 7647,  -- Undulating umbrils! What in the world was that!?
        IT_SEEMS_THIS_ISLAND_HAS_BEEN_INFILTRATED_BY                          = 7648,  -- ...It seems this island has been infiltrated by an insidious instigator, kupo.
        I_M_SURE_THAT_HE_S_THE_ONE                                            = 7649,  -- I'm sure that he's the one responsible for that headward-hurtling harvest mere moments ago!
        WE_MUST_TAKE_UP_ARMS_AGAINST_THIS_ANONYMOUS                           = 7650,  -- We must take up arms against this anonymous assailant before he can spread his tenebrous tendrils any further. Make haste and cleave that crag in twain to obtain %, kupo!
        WHILE_YOU_RE_WHITTLING_AWAY_AT_THAT_WHETSTONE                         = 7651,  -- While you're whittling away at that whetstone, I'll start in on a snare.
        A_ROTTEN_REPROBATE_S_BEEN_RUNNING_AROUND_LIKE                         = 7652,  -- A rotten reprobate's been running around like a rogue in the Mog Garden, kupo.
        TO_STOP_THIS_SORRY_SOD_WE_LL_NEED                                     = 7653,  -- To stop this sorry sod, we'll need % from that bulky boulder beyond. Once you get it, make me aware and we'll go from there.
        HIP_HIP_HOORAY_KUPO_WITH_THIS_WE_CAN                                  = 7654,  -- Hip, hip, hooray, kupo! With this %, we can smother, smash, and smear that smug stowaway into oblivion!
        NOW_GO_OUT_THERE_AND_GARROTE_HIM_I                                    = 7655,  -- Now go out there and garrote him, %! I'll stay back and serve as your sturdy supporting stanchion, kupo.
        I_D_LOVE_TO_HELP_WITH_PUMMELING_THAT                                  = 7656,  -- I'd love to help with pummeling that pernicious punk, but we're preeminent pacifists. It's contrary to our character to lash out against living things. I wish you the best in battle, though, kupo!
        DO_MY_EARS_DECEIVE_ME_OR_IS_SOMETHING                                 = 7657,  -- Do my ears deceive me, or is something stirring in yonder pond, kupo?
        TERRIFIC_TIMING_LET_S_LAUNCH_INTO_A_NEW                               = 7658,  -- Terrific timing! Let's launch into a new lesson by letting you lift the net sitting silently in the pond over there.
        FISH_UP_ALL_THE_FRESHWATER_FARE_YOU_CAN                               = 7659,  -- Fish up all the freshwater fare you can, including that craven criminal, kupo!
        NURSE_THE_NETTING_OUT_OF_THE_SWELLING_SPRING                          = 7660,  -- Nurse the netting out of the swelling spring to see if that evil entity got entangled in it.
        SHOULD_YOU_FIND_FISHY_FRAGMENTS_OR_ANYTHING_AT                        = 7661,  -- Should you find fishy fragments--or anything at all--apprise me as soon as you're able, kupo.
        POWER_TO_THE_PIONEERS_KUPO_YOU_VE_SUCCESSFULLY                        = 7662,  -- Power to the pioneers, kupo! You've successfully seized the catch of the day!
        OR_NOT_I_NEVER_KNEW_THE_NUMBERS_OF                                    = 7663,  -- ...Or not? I never knew the numbers of fish were so negligible here.
        KUPOPOPO_WHY_THERE_S_A_GAPING_GASH_THE                                = 7664,  -- Kupopopo? Why, there's a gaping gash the size of Marjami Ravine in this net! It must be the work of that wicked wanderer!
        KUPAH_PER_PIP_UUUGH_HE_S_GOT_ME                                       = 7665,  -- Kupah-per-pip... Uuugh, he's got me so flustered that I can't even string together a simple sentence, kupo!
        THE_SCOUNDREL_SLUNK_OFF_INTO_THE_SEA_FOR                              = 7666,  -- The scoundrel slunk off into the sea, for certain.
        THERE_S_ANOTHER_NET_SPECIFICALLY_SET_UP_FOR                           = 7667,  -- There's another net specifically set up for obtaining all the ocean has to offer, kupo.
        QUICK_BEFORE_HE_CUTS_THAT_TOO_I_LL                                    = 7668,  -- Quick, before he cuts that, too! I'll find you after I finish fixing these frayed fish fetters. Just hurry!
        UNFORGIVABLE_THAT_CONTEMPTIBLE_CUR_HAS_RILED_UP_THE                   = 7669,  -- Unforgivable... That contemptible cur has riled up the unbridled wrath of myriad moogles all Mog Gardens over, kupoooooo!
        WE_SEALED_AWAY_ANY_SCINTILLA_OF_SEETHING_RAGE                         = 7670,  -- We sealed away any scintilla of seething rage that might swell to the surface of our souls long ago, but now is the time to shun our self-imposed shackles and make him pay with every fiber of our fur!
        IT_S_DETESTABLE_DEPLORABLE_DESPICABLE_EVEN_NO_ONE                     = 7671,  -- It's detestable, deplorable, despicable even! No one pillages this paradise from perimeter to pole and gets away with it, kupo!
        WHAT_WAS_THAT_POLES_AND_PERIMETERS_AREN_T                             = 7672,  -- What was that? Poles and perimeters aren't perfectly paired, and this profligate isn't pillaging per se, kupo?
        NO_MATTER_JUST_NUDGE_THE_NETTING_THAT_S                               = 7673,  -- No matter, just nudge the netting that's sitting near the sandy shore and come calling when you've finished.
        KUPOOOOOOOOO                                                          = 7674,  -- Kupooooooooo...
        I_VE_DESCRIED_THY_DECEPTIONS_AND_SHALL_DUTIFULLY                      = 7675,  -- I've descried thy deceptions and shall dutifully deliver thy quietus, kupo!
        IT_WAS_YOU_WHO_SOWED_THE_SINISTER_SEEDS                               = 7676,  -- It was you who sowed the sinister seeds of discord and danger in our delightful Mog Garden!
        HOW_DARE_YOU_THREATEN_ME_WITH_THOSE_PATHETIC                          = 7677,  -- How dare you threaten me with those pathetic pustules of pincers? For that, I shall show you no quarter, nor will I make the affair quiet, kupo!
