        CHACHAROON_S_CHEER_IS_AN_ABILITY_THAT_CHANGES                         = 8627,  -- Chacharoon's Cheer is an ability that changes the power of trust, love, and friendship into special abilities based on manipulating a monster's myriad memories, kupo.
