        SHEEP_ARE_PEACEFUL_AND_OBEDIENT_ANIMALS_WHICH_EXPLAINS                = 8644,  -- Sheep are peaceful and obedient animals, which explains why they are often recommended to fledgling ranchers. Others who have cared for them in the past note that it is possible to receive % from them.
        RESIDENTS_OF_WINDURST_AND_ITS_SURROUNDING_AREAS_HAVE                  = 8645,  -- Residents of Windurst and its surrounding areas have been known to keep rabbits, or rarabs in the local vernacular. These omnivorous animals supposedly relinquish % to their trainers on certain occasions, but such reports have yet to be verified.
        TREANTS_CAN_THRIVE_IN_MANY_DIFFERENT_CLIMES_BUT                       = 8646,  -- Treants can thrive in many different climes, but no matter the location, occasionally impart % to those who look after them...if anything.
        LIZARDS_ARE_FOUND_THROUGH_ALL_CLIMES_AND_ELEVATIONS                   = 8647,  -- Lizards are found through all climes and elevations in Vana'diel, from the harshest deserts to the snowiest peaks. Such resilient creatures are known to bequeath % to their caretakers.
        COCKATRICES_ARE_CARNIVOROUS_BIRDS_FOUND_IN_SOME_OF                    = 8648,  -- Cockatrices are carnivorous birds found in some of Vana'diel's least hospitable locales, but recent domestication efforts have begun to bear fruit. Be wary to keep some gloves handy when handling the % they offer their owners.
        RAPTORS_ARE_QUICK_WITTED_VICIOUS_LITTLE_BUGGERS_WHO                   = 8649,  -- Raptors are quick-witted, vicious little buggers who can often be found feasting on flesh in mountainous areas and on the tops of precarious plateaus. As one would expect of such ravenous beasts, tamers can often procure % from them.
        EFTS_THRIVE_IN_WATERSIDE_LOCATIONS_AND_ARE_OFTEN                      = 8650,  -- Efts thrive in waterside locations, and are often spotted munching on prey in Bibiki Bay. Take caution not to get any % on your hands when you touch them!
        DHALMELS_ARE_DOCILE_DOMESTICATED_CREATURES_THAT_LIVE_IN               = 8651,  -- Dhalmels are docile, domesticated creatures that live in arid climes, grazing on the sparse vegetation that dots the landscape. A conscientious master may be able to procure % from them.
        THE_SALT_WATER_DWELLING_SEA_MONKS_PREY_ON                             = 8652,  -- The salt water-dwelling sea monks prey on smaller species of fish and have been known to be highly territorial come spawning season. Those who treat them right have been known to receive % on occasion.
        URAGNITES_RESIDE_IN_BIBIKI_BAY_AND_THE_ULBUKAN                        = 8653,  -- Uragnites reside in Bibiki Bay and the Ulbukan coastline, and their diet of krill helps keep the ecosystem in check. Properly caring for one could yield a reasonable amount of %.
        NARY_A_BODY_OF_WATER_FROM_THE_DEEPEST                                 = 8654,  -- Nary a body of water, from the deepest oceans to the most humid marshlands, is without the presence of crabs in some shape or form. They tear their pray in half with pincers before feasting--a most gruesome scene in the best of times. The meek members of the species, however, may impart % upon their owners.
        COLIBRIS_ARE_NATIVE_TO_WESTERN_AHT_URHGAN_AND                         = 8655,  -- Colibris are native to western Aht Urhgan, and are among the fiercest and most aggressive birds known to man. Should they be tamed, however, they may bestow % upon those who treated them well.
        COEURLS_ARE_FEROCIOUS_CARNIVORES_OFTEN_FOUND_PROWLING_MINDARTIA       = 8656,  -- Coeurls are ferocious carnivores often found prowling Mindartia and Elshimo. Taming them could yield a sizable quantity of %.
        THE_LAND_OF_AHT_URHGAN_IS_HOME_TO                                     = 8657,  -- The land of Aht Urhgan is home to buffalo, hulking herbivores that are easy to rear thanks to their docile nature. Those with particularly strong affinities for their masters are known to give them %.
        SLIMES_ARE_AMORPHOUS_MONSTERS_THAT_TEND_TO_PREFER                     = 8658,  -- Slimes are amorphous monsters that tend to prefer the dank, dark atmosphere of caves. Go spelunking with them and hope they give you % in the process.
        BUGARDS_OFTEN_FOUND_ON_THE_TAVNAZIAN_ARCHIPELAGO_WILL                 = 8659,  -- Bugards, often found on the Tavnazian Archipelago, will chow down on anything they can get their hands on. Those rearing these creatures are advised to keep a close eye on their belongings when they try to procure items such as % from them.
        ADAMANTOISES_ARE_CONCERNED_WITH_NOTHING_BUT_BALLOONING_UP             = 8660,  -- Adamantoises are concerned with nothing but ballooning up until they are the size of a mountain, and those rearing them should take care to keep their size to a minimum. None can say what types of items can be procured from them.
        BOMBS_ARE_LIVING_MAGICAL_ENTITIES_WHO_HAVE_BEEN                       = 8661,  -- Bombs are living magical entities who have been known to explode on more than one hapless adventurer. Treated well, they will hesitantly bequeath % to their masters.
        BEHEMOTHS_ARE_KNOWN_TO_PROWL_THE_INNERMOST_RECESSES                   = 8662,  -- Behemoths are known to prowl the innermost recesses of the Qufim region, and are perhaps the most ferocious representatives of the beast family. Those taking the proper precautions in caring for them may be able to receive %.
        THESE_STRANGE_AMBULATORY_CACTI_ARE_COMMONLY_FOUND_IN                  = 8663,  -- These strange, ambulatory cacti are commonly found in the Altepa Desert of the Kuzotz Region. Sabotenders are relentlessly aggressive when provoked, perhaps explaining why so little regarding their way of life is known to science.
